creator: Franklin Community Church, Indiana
descriptionHtml:
This app is packed with powerful content and resources to help you grow and stay connected. With this app you can:

- Watch or listen to past messages

- Stay up-to-date with Push Notifications

- Share your favorite messages via Twitter, Facebook, or email

- Download messages for offline listening

- Follow along with our Bible Reading Plan

- Sign up for events

- Make a secure gift
descriptionShort: Powerful content and resources to help you grow and stay connected.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: If enabled, the app will show the viewer a prompt to take an action at a designated time during a live stream.

title: My FCC

creator: Franklin Community Church, Indiana
descriptionHtml:
The FCC app helps you Cultivating Christ-Centered Community in a digital space! Download the app now to assist in your spiritual and communal growth as well as engage with Franklin Community Church. On the app, you can...

- Find our Sunday morning livestream!
- Listen/watch past sermons!
- Submit prayer requests!
- Join 15 min. Online Prayer Times!
- View and sign up for upcoming events!
- Listen to an audio Bible
- More!
descriptionShort: Cultivating Christ-Centered Community in a digital space

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Messaging users can report content and other users to their administrators
- Groups can require manager approval to join
- Misc. bug fixes and improvements
